me":"2020-06-07T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"49a0b53bfcf73c651ad26a1ea3c8f5ee33c8ea6b","tid":2055094,"uid":235814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"一人一句你聽過最廢嘅廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab6865d233a06ce09a1ead7e334adcf5c8f912c","tid":2055094,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"你老母無錯呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係搞笑啲啫"},{"pid":"fcb64e5758a7c0fd4080cb3fc47cc853b5d5d35f","tid":2055094,"uid":191651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a0b53bfcf73c651ad26a1ea3c8f5ee33c8ea6b","tid":2055094,"uid":235814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"一人一句你聽過最廢嘅廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"都幾好笑 2/10"},{"pid":"a29e61ec15af166efb9a45fddfe2acac9312a9ae","tid":2055094,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"感情台回覆：「每對情侶 / 個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此乃over-specification<br />\n一句中止別人討論嘅萬能廢話+所有戀愛專家/po被一句收皮<br />\n見親都燥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n也許相愛很難<br />\n就難在其實雙方各有各寄望 怎麼辦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n要單戀都難<br />\n受太大的禮會内疚卻也無力歸還<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n也許不愛不難<br />\n但如未成佛升仙也會怕愛情前途黯淡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n愛不愛都難<br />\n未快樂先有責任給予對方面露歡顏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n得到浪漫又要有空間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n得到定局即怕去到終站<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n然後付出多得到少不介意豁達<br />\n又擔心有人看不過眼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span>"},{"pid":"c90204b6bcf4380c5bdb6752c166629bb2064fef","tid":2055094,"uid":191651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a29e61ec15af166efb9a45fddfe2acac9312a9ae","tid":2055094,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"感情台回覆：「每對情侶 / 個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n此乃over-specification<br />\n一句中止別人討論嘅萬能廢話+所有戀愛專家/po被一句收皮<br />\n見親都燥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n也許相愛很難<br />\n就難在其實雙方各有各寄望 怎麼辦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n要單戀都難<br />\n受太大的禮會内疚卻也無力歸還<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n也許不愛不難<br />\n但如未成佛升仙也會怕愛情前途黯淡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n愛不愛都難<br />\n未快樂先有責任給予對方面露歡顏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n得到浪漫又要有空間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n得到定局即怕去到終站<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span><br />\n然後付出多得到少不介意豁達<br />\n又擔心有人看不過眼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"戴頭盔"},{"pid":"a47d047fcf3cce598a234a78eca6dbfd7989e6ab","tid":2055094,"uid":191651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4a53f8048bb49974131b698e4ac82c8af5582e28","tid":2055094,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c90204b6bcf4380c5bdb6752c166629bb2064fef","tid":2055094,"uid":191651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a29e61ec15af166efb9a45fddfe2acac9312a9ae","tid":2055094,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"感情台回覆：「每對情侶 / 個個人都唔同，唔可以一概而論。」<img